response.overview: Club Jenna's latest star bursts into her premiere flick with all the hunger of a cat in heat. Join this Asian pixie and her partners in corruption for an all new film featuring some of the messiest sex you've ever swallowed! Fresh from her blazing hot win on Jenna's American Sex Star, British sensation Roxy Jezel pops her Club Jenna cherry in style. Hang onto your helmet as Roxy proves her recklessness on a racy motorcycle ride with Tommy Gunn, then speeds off to take Mario Rossi for a whirl that explodes in a drippy facial - call out the clean up crew for this one! And are you ready for some girl-on-girl action? Roxy is! Her interoffice tryst with sweetheart Sammie Rhodes becomes a lesson in putting her money where her mouth is. But it doesn't end there ... Join Cindy Crawford, Kinzie Kenner, Eva Angelina, and more of your favorite stars for some out of this world action - and get in line to see who's been rocking Roxy!
response.tagline: The American Sex Star winner pops her Club Jenna cherry!
response.title: Rockin' Roxy
